641
01:03:53,892 --> 01:03:57,140
A program named Zuse, who
fought along side the ISO's.

642
01:03:57,115 --> 01:04:01,115
They say he can get anyone anywhere..

643
01:04:02,030 --> 01:04:03,525
How do I find him?

644
01:04:06,884 --> 01:04:08,357
This is his sector.

645
01:04:12,078 --> 01:04:13,722
Make it there alive.

646
01:04:13,723 --> 01:04:14,988
And he'll find you.

647
01:04:55,866 --> 01:04:56,906
Sam.

648
01:05:00,679 --> 01:05:02,036
Sam?

649
01:05:44,022 --> 01:05:46,166
Hey man, it's your lucky day.

650
01:05:54,785 --> 01:05:55,875
Stop it.

651
01:06:06,341 --> 01:06:07,775
Sam Flynn.

652
01:06:08,980 --> 01:06:11,043
-You remember me.
-Yeah.

653
01:06:11,044 --> 01:06:13,169
You gave me some advice.

654
01:06:13,170 --> 01:06:14,473
And you followed it.

655
01:06:15,362 --> 01:06:17,559
Its unfortunate we met the way we did.

656
01:06:19,423 --> 01:06:20,817
You have a good night.

657
01:06:20,981 --> 01:06:22,449
You're looking for someone.

658
01:06:25,874 --> 01:06:27,547
What makes you say that.

659
01:06:28,692 --> 01:06:30,189
Intuition.

660
01:06:32,827 --> 01:06:35,250
Sir, sentries down town,

661
01:06:35,251 --> 01:06:37,003
recovered Flynn's light cycle.

662
01:06:38,274 --> 01:06:40,743
They've traced it to it's component of origin.

663
01:07:06,441 --> 01:07:08,523
Prepare the light-runner Quorra.

664
01:07:10,287 --> 01:07:11,701
We're going downtown.

665
01:07:34,728 --> 01:07:36,761
Thank you for bringing my son to me.

666
01:07:37,067 --> 01:07:41,124
Flynn, you don't need to go. I sent
him to someone we can trust.

667
01:07:41,125 --> 01:07:43,240
Quorra, there is no choice.

668
01:07:44,088 --> 01:07:45,978
I won't lose him again.

669
01:07:48,304 --> 01:07:51,992
Chaos, good news.

670
01:08:32,992 --> 01:08:35,316
Relax, they're off the grid.

671
01:08:42,281 --> 01:08:43,812
His name is Castor.

672
01:08:43,813 --> 01:08:46,403
You want to speak to Zuse you're
going to have to go to him.

673
01:08:46,404 --> 01:08:48,502
Where is your sense of humor, my friend?

674
01:08:48,503 --> 01:08:51,893
Programs are disappearing, Castor. Soon
none of us will be left.

675
01:08:51,894 --> 01:08:55,020
Zuse can make the factions, ferment the revolution.

676
01:08:55,021 --> 01:08:57,050
Well of course Zuse can do these things.

677
01:08:57,051 --> 01:08:58,713
Grant me an audience.

678
01:08:58,714 --> 01:09:01,649
Your enthusiasm is intoxicating
my dear bot,

679
01:09:01,650 --> 01:09:04,479
But Zuse's time is precious.

680
01:09:04,480 --> 01:09:06,743
We shall see.

681
01:09:10,819 --> 01:09:13,497
If you'll excuse me a moment, I have to, uh...

682
01:09:14,379 --> 01:09:16,780
Attend to something, but have a drink.

683
01:09:17,154 --> 01:09:19,557
Courtesy of the "End of line" club.

684
01:09:20,062 --> 01:09:21,162
It is happening.

685
01:09:21,163 --> 01:09:24,260
Come, away from these primitive functions.

686
01:09:25,355 --> 01:09:27,775
The son of Flynn.

687
01:09:27,776 --> 01:09:30,465
Of all the innumerable possibilities.

688
01:09:30,534 --> 01:09:32,990
He has to walk into mine.

689
01:09:33,709 --> 01:09:38,767
Libations, for everybody!

690
01:09:40,700 --> 01:09:42,458
I'm Castor.

691
01:09:42,948 --> 01:09:44,278
Your host.

692
01:09:44,362 --> 01:09:49,604
Provider of any and all entertainment
and diversions.

693
01:09:49,610 --> 01:09:50,945
At your service.

694
01:09:53,552 --> 01:09:55,081
I'm looking for Zuse.

695
01:09:55,688 --> 01:09:56,981
Indeed.

696
01:09:57,082 --> 01:09:58,587
Many are.

697
01:09:59,133 --> 01:10:00,516
Where can I find him?

698
01:10:01,200 --> 01:10:05,192
This pretty miss, is a conversation
best had behind closed doors.

699
01:10:05,193 --> 01:10:08,276
Perhaps we should retire to
my private lounge.

700
01:10:10,465 --> 01:10:13,233
Uh, designed it myself, you know.

701
01:10:13,234 --> 01:10:14,649
It's true.

702
01:10:14,650 --> 01:10:17,211
I'm stepping away for a moment, boys.

703
01:10:17,212 --> 01:10:19,426
Change the scheme, alter the mood.

704
01:10:19,427 --> 01:10:23,886
Electrify the boys and girls,
if you'd be so kind.

705
01:10:26,825 --> 01:10:27,949
Thank you.

706
01:10:27,950 --> 01:10:29,159
Gem.

707
01:10:29,160 --> 01:10:30,711
My name is, Gem.

708
01:11:12,582 --> 01:11:14,067
Ah, perfect.

709
01:12:34,483 --> 01:12:37,116
-You are CLU.
-I am CLU.

710
01:12:37,117 --> 01:12:39,875
You will create the perfect system.

711
01:12:39,876 --> 01:12:41,943
I will create the perfect system.

712
01:12:45,900 --> 01:12:48,451
Together we're going to change the world, man.

713
01:12:56,197 --> 01:12:57,880
(Angrily screams)

714
01:13:15,749 --> 01:13:17,456
Let's move.

715
01:13:19,213 --> 01:13:23,155
Zuse has been around since the earliest
days of the gaming grid.

716
01:13:23,507 --> 01:13:27,443
By necessity.
Castor mined all the percentages.

717
01:13:27,823 --> 01:13:29,280
All the angles.

718
01:13:29,281 --> 01:13:30,988
So when do I meet him?

719
01:13:34,111 --> 01:13:36,960
You...just...did.

720
01:13:40,472 --> 01:13:44,282
After the purge, I needed
to reinvent myself.

721
01:13:44,513 --> 01:13:46,541
Self preservation, you understand.

722
01:13:52,128 --> 01:13:53,143
Now.

723
01:13:54,538 --> 01:13:56,993
