724
01:13:59,276 --> 01:14:01,176
I need to get to the portal.

725
01:14:01,637 --> 01:14:03,686
Well, it's closing quickly.

726
01:14:03,687 --> 01:14:05,233
As I'm sure, you're aware.

727
01:14:05,672 --> 01:14:07,238
Tick-tock, tick-tock.

728
01:14:07,518 --> 01:14:09,438
And it's quite a journey.

729
01:14:09,969 --> 01:14:12,701
Beyond the far reaches of the outland.

730
01:14:13,069 --> 01:14:18,507
Your father didn't want any programs,
slipping out accidentally, did he.

731
01:14:18,673 --> 01:14:19,881
Can you help me?

732
01:14:20,335 --> 01:14:22,179
Of course.

733
01:14:22,991 --> 01:14:27,074
