on staying well informed.

734
01:14:27,075 --> 01:14:29,052
I must ask, who sent you my way?

735
01:14:32,660 --> 01:14:33,802
Her name's, Quorra.

736
01:14:34,724 --> 01:14:36,720
Said she met you a long time ago.

737
01:14:37,379 --> 01:14:38,922
I believe she did.

738
01:14:40,079 --> 01:14:41,790
Many cycles ago.

739
01:14:42,964 --> 01:14:44,838
Was a different time.

740
01:14:45,594 --> 01:14:48,065
But we're not here to relive the past.

741
01:14:48,066 --> 01:14:49,765
Let's see about your future, shall we?

742
01:14:49,766 --> 01:14:51,014
Now, well have to, uh...

743
01:14:51,015 --> 01:14:53,832
change your attire, and you'll need
a forged disc.

744
01:14:53,833 --> 01:14:54,995
