745
01:14:54,996 --> 01:14:57,937
But my. And of  course you'll need transport.

746
01:14:58,995 --> 01:15:01,111
To cross the sea of simulation.

747
01:15:12,429 --> 01:15:15,083
This is going to be quite a ride.

748
01:15:27,737 --> 01:15:30,113
I believed in users once before.

749
01:15:31,179 --> 01:15:32,932
Playing all the angles.

750
01:15:37,681 --> 01:15:39,290
Revenge!

751
01:15:47,717 --> 01:15:49,666
The game has changed.

752
01:15:49,667 --> 01:15:51,280
Son of Flynn!

753
01:16:01,274 --> 01:16:03,288
Ha, ha, haaa.

754
01:16:08,124 --> 01:16:09,193
Met your friend.

755
01:16:09,194 --> 01:16:10,477
He's fantastic.

756
01:16:10,478 --> 01:16:14,528
Behold, the son of our maker.

757
01:16:42,230 --> 01:16:43,680
Yeah, yeah.

758
01:17:24,381 --> 01:17:25,558
Goes through ....

