Dad, it's gone.

763
01:18:32,029 --> 01:18:33,180
It is.

764
01:18:36,030 --> 01:18:37,933
I'm sorry, I know I messed up.

765
01:18:39,813 --> 01:18:41,503
We can go back, I can go back.

766
01:18:41,504 --> 01:18:43,122
No, we stay together.

767
01:18:43,720 --> 01:18:44,847
Dad, I can do this.

768
01:18:44,848 --> 01:18:46,563
You've done enough all ready.

769
01:18:52,182 --> 01:18:54,431
Sam, you really.

