797
01:21:08,353 --> 01:21:11,693
In our world, she could change everything.

798
01:21:18,723 --> 01:21:20,821
Check that out.

799
01:21:28,498 --> 01:21:30,759
She risked herself for me.

800
01:21:32,385 --> 01:21:34,383
Some things are worth the risk.

801
01:21:48,148 --> 01:21:49,811
Look at this.

802
01:21:52,669 --> 01:21:57,295
Now that is impressive, if I do say
so myself, huh?

803
01:21:58,151 --> 01:22:01,572
Come on, it's going to take a while for
